  "detailed_description": "\"Just Drift It !\" is a cool little game with custom vehicle physics based on realistic tire model and advanced suspension !<br />\r\n\"Just Drift It !\" is all about mastering controls and getting better trying to beat you best score and get higher in the leaderboards !<br />\r\nSo have fun and... \"Just Drift It\" !<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* 12 vehicles<br />\r\n* Ghost system<br />\r\n* Replay system<br />\r\n* Paint car parts<br />\r\n* Local audio player<br />\r\n* Custom Vehicle Physics<br />\r\n* Tuning parameters for suspension, Gearbox, Wheel alignment ( camber angle ) and others...<br />\r\n* Freeroam mode<br />\r\n* Career mode<br />\r\n* Leaderborads<br />\r\n* Controller support",
  "about_the_game": "\"Just Drift It !\" is a cool little game with custom vehicle physics based on realistic tire model and advanced suspension !<br />\r\n\"Just Drift It !\" is all about mastering controls and getting better trying to beat you best score and get higher in the leaderboards !<br />\r\nSo have fun and... \"Just Drift It\" !<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* 12 vehicles<br />\r\n* Ghost system<br />\r\n* Replay system<br />\r\n* Paint car parts<br />\r\n* Local audio player<br />\r\n* Custom Vehicle Physics<br />\r\n* Tuning parameters for suspension, Gearbox, Wheel alignment ( camber angle ) and others...<br />\r\n* Freeroam mode<br />\r\n* Career mode<br />\r\n* Leaderborads<br />\r\n* Controller support",
